        <li>image-&gt;wilting plants [circumstance_phrase]</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase-&gt;near a [terrainfeature]</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase-&gt;close to [terrainfeature]</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase-&gt;around the dying countryside of [community]</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase-&gt;between [terrainfeature] and a [terrainfeature]</li>
        <li>desc_sentence-&gt;In the dust, [pawn_nameShortDef] plays [game] with a [friendlyadjective] look.</li>
        <li>desc_sentence-&gt;[pawn_nameShortDef] prays for rain, need on [pawn_possessive] face.</li>
        <li>desc_sentence-&gt;[quantity_adjphrase] [outlander]s watch from below.</li>
        <li>desc_sentence-&gt;[pawn_nameShortDef] sits near a [terrainfeature], pouring dried dirt through [pawn_possessive] fingers.</li>
        <li>desc_sentence-&gt;[quantity_adjphrase] [animal]s are leaving the area, or dying of thirst.</li>
        <li>desc_sentence-&gt;There is no [enemy] in sight.</li>
